  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2748600/extras/2cc3f5cc3e922b8bbc0160e3d87aaf2e.avif?t=1753344608\" width=1600 height=900 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Overdrive Warfare is an FPS shooter developed by Dynamite Games. Immerse yourself in the first chapter of the Overdrive universe as Task Force Scorpion unite with the Lumar Republic to fight a relentless threat known as the Zarya Group.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2748600/extras/d2ee74e537211b6300df9ff8e71924c5.avif?t=1753344608\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2748600/extras_big/d2ee74e537211b6300df9ff8e71924c5.avif?t=1753344608 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight your way through the war-torn environments of the once peaceful Lumar Isle in this fast-paced arena shooter with a variety of weapon attachments, player modifications and customization options becoming available as you level up.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2748600/extras/98ddafaf5f00dde1ebfffcd8c2b4569d.avif?t=1753344608\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2748600/extras_big/98ddafaf5f00dde1ebfffcd8c2b4569d.avif?t=1753344608 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drop into the hottest Zarya Group occupied territory, Zarya Isle, to be the last one standing. Collect loot, explore the military-occupied isle and survive against a rapidly shrinking safe zone.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2748600/extras/2cc3f5cc3e922b8bbc0160e3d87aaf2e.avif?t=1753344608\" width=1600 height=900 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Overdrive Warfare is an FPS shooter developed by Dynamite Games. Immerse yourself in the first chapter of the Overdrive universe as Task Force Scorpion unite with the Lumar Republic to fight a relentless threat known as the Zarya Group.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2748600/extras/d2ee74e537211b6300df9ff8e71924c5.avif?t=1753344608\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2748600/extras_big/d2ee74e537211b6300df9ff8e71924c5.avif?t=1753344608 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight your way through the war-torn environments of the once peaceful Lumar Isle in this fast-paced arena shooter with a variety of weapon attachments, player modifications and customization options becoming available as you level up.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2748600/extras/98ddafaf5f00dde1ebfffcd8c2b4569d.avif?t=1753344608\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2748600/extras_big/98ddafaf5f00dde1ebfffcd8c2b4569d.avif?t=1753344608 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drop into the hottest Zarya Group occupied territory, Zarya Isle, to be the last one standing. Collect loot, explore the military-occupied isle and survive against a rapidly shrinking safe zone.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
